@startuml
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Manager:in" as Manager
actor "Administrator:in" as Admin
participant "Mobile App" as App
participant "Express API" as Api
database "SQLite" as DB

Manager -> App : Aenderung erfassen
App -> Api : POST /api/manager/change-requests
Api -> DB : Request mit Status PENDING speichern
Api --> App : Request bestaetigen

Admin -> App : offene Antraege anzeigen
App -> Api : GET /api/admin/change-requests
Api -> DB : Requests laden
DB --> Api : Liste
Api --> App : Liste

Admin -> App : Antrag annehmen
App -> Api : POST /api/admin/change-requests/{id}/approve
Api -> DB : Payload auf Zielentitaet anwenden
Api -> DB : Status APPROVED setzen
Api --> App : Ergebnis
@enduml
